data.description: 3 bed/2.5 home on 1 acre lot with finished basement and fenced backyard in established neighborhood with NO HOA in the highly sought WALNUT GROVE SCHOOL DISTRICT. Hardwoods and tile floors throughout! Foyer entrance opens up to grand 2 story family room with masonry fireplace and lots of natural light. Large eat-in kitchen features granite counters, stainless steel appliances and bay window. Separate dining room and half bath complete the downstairs. Upstairs you'll find a true primary suite- complete with trey ceilings, double vanity, walk-in closet, soaking tub and separate shower. 2 additional bedrooms and full bathrooms in Jack and Jill set up. Basement has a finished room with bar- perfect man cave or media room, could even be used as a 4th bedroom! Basement also has large work shop area with boat door. Rocking chair front porch and huge back deck provide plenty of space to enjoy the outdoors and entertain guests. Storage shed and 2 carports will remain. Septic was pumped, riser added and field lines drained just 2 months ago. Property is USDA eligible! Professional photos coming soon!
